        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "You have felt their malice, then. The Oathbreakers of the Dimholt will answer only to the heir of Isildur, and only to the blade that was Narsil reforged -- Anduril, the Flame of the West, which I bear. I do not lend it lightly. Prove yourself worthy: destroy the Witch-king of Angmar, chief of the Nine, and bring me proof of his end. Then the blade is yours."
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "__struct_id": 2,
