        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "The iron crown, broken at last... so the witch is truly unmade. Few could have done it. Take it, then -- Anduril, Flame of the West. Bear it to the Dimholt and give the Dead their long-denied rest."
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "__struct_id": 3,
        "Animation": {
